    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="0">
        <title>Heater-Cab With Pro Sleeper</title>
        <para>The heater/air conditioning system has a blower motor circuit and a compressor control circuit. The
            compressor control circuit is tied to the blower motor circuit which can be set to off, low, medium or high
            speed to circulate heating or cooling air throughout the cab.
        </para>
